<div style="float: left; margin-left: 0.9em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;"><figure class="mw-halign-right" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/Afaylu:L%C9%9Bammt_n_i%E1%B8%A5uddjin.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/64/L%C9%9Bammt_n_i%E1%B8%A5uddjin.jpg/250px-L%C9%9Bammt_n_i%E1%B8%A5uddjin.jpg" decoding="async" width="250" height="150" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/64/L%C9%9Bammt_n_i%E1%B8%A5uddjin.jpg/330px-L%C9%9Bammt_n_i%E1%B8%A5uddjin.jpg 2x" data-file-width="800" data-file-height="480"></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p><b>Lɛammt</b> tga yan wanaw n <a href="/wiki/Ta%E1%BA%93u%E1%B9%9Bi" title="Taẓuṛi">tẓuṛi</a> tamaziɣt iwtn s iẓuṛan g umzruy n ufgan amaziɣ tasut f tasut, tga taẓuṛi n <a href="/w/index.php?title=A%E1%B9%9Bka%E1%B8%8D&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Aṛkaḍ (ur tlli tasna ad)">uṛkaḍ</a>  imunn d <a href="/wiki/Tan%E1%B8%8D%E1%B8%8Damt" title="Tanḍḍamt">nnḍm</a>, tg s yat tgmiḍi iggutn taẓuṛi n irgazn.  taẓuṛi ad tlla dar tugt n tqqbilin g <a href="/wiki/Lm%C9%A3rib" title="Lmɣrib">Lmɣrib</a>. Tettyussan bahra lɛammt g tqqbilt n <a href="/wiki/Imf%E1%B8%8Dwak" class="mw-redirect" title="Imfḍwak">infḍwak</a> iwalan i <a href="/wiki/Tamna%E1%B8%8Dt_n_Azilal" class="mw-redirect" title="Tamnaḍt n Azilal">tamnaḍt n Uzilal</a>, <a href="/wiki/Tasga_n_Bni_Mllal-Xnifra" class="mw-redirect" title="Tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifra">tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifṛa</a>. Lɛammt tga taẓuṛi iẓlin s tqqbilt n infḍwak, tlla lɛammt ula g mnnawt n tmnaḍin n tqqbilt n <a href="/w/index.php?title=I%C9%A3jdamn&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Iɣjdamn (ur tlli tasna ad)">iɣjdamn</a> inmalan d tqqbilt n infḍwak sg tsga n iffus utrim. . Ism ad n lɛammt illa g tmizar yaḍni zun <a href="/w/index.php?title=%E1%BA%92ayyan&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Ẓayyan (ur tlli tasna ad)">Ẓayyan</a> d <a href="/wiki/Sus" title="Sus">Sus</a> macc idrus, acku darsn anawn yaḍnin n tẓuṛi, Sus gis <a href="/wiki/A%E1%B8%A5wac" title="Aḥwac">Aḥwac</a>, Ẓayyan nutni ar tturarn s <a href="/wiki/A%E1%B8%A5idus" title="Aḥidus">Uḥidus</a>. Tettuyssan Lɛammt s ismawn yaḍni zun "Lɛmmt" d "Lɛammat".
</p><p>Ar tettyawskar Lɛammt akud nna illa kra n uzmzzu iẓlin s tqqbilt nɣ s kra n usun nɣ aḍwwaṛ, zun ig tlla tmɣra dar usli nɣ taslit, ttlgit (anmuggur da skarn middn i lɛaml, lqqayd nɣ kra n ubṛlamani) n kra wudm imqqurn, asfuglu s kra n uzmzzu n tsrtit zun istayn nɣ kra n <a href="/wiki/Imn%C9%A3i" title="Imnɣi">imnɣi</a>. G irir n Lɛammt ar ttbddadn tugt n irgazn ar skarn adur, lsn <a href="/wiki/Tajllabit" title="Tajllabit">tijlluba</a> nɣ lfuqqiyyat tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin (idrus ma g ttilint g kra n ukʷlu yaḍn), d <a href="/wiki/Aduku" title="Aduku">idukan</a> d titqacrin(ar asnt ttinin ttqqacṛ) ula nttnti g ma iggutn ar ttggant tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin, gn f yixf nnsn <a href="/w/index.php?title=Acddad&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Acddad (ur tlli tasna ad)">acddad</a> nɣ taṛẓẓit (ar as ttinin infḍwak ṛṛẓṭ) tawṛaɣt nɣ tumlilt nɣ ar lssan f ixfawn nnsn tacacit (nɣ ṭṭagiyya) ula nttat g ukʷlu umlil nɣ awraɣ; agʷln g iɣariwn (nɣ iɣṛaḍ) nnsn lkʷmmit, ku argaz ar dis isatti allun nɣ tallunt nns nɣ ar ittḥuc ɣar s ifassn nns, yili ditsn ula bab n ganga, ar ssntayn (nɣ ar bddun) irgazn llɣa nɣ tanḍḍamt ar kkatn allun ar ig iḥma ilmma kcmn d tfrxin (ar asnt ttinin timḥwacin) ilsan lqqṭib d tmlsa tiblday n tmazirt skrnt ula nttnti adur nnsnt dat adur n irgazn macc ur a ditsn ttxllaḍn ar ig ssrɣan lɛammt ilmma ku argaz ar d ilddi yat tfruxt ad dis ittḥuc. Tifrxin ar ttḥucnt s ifassn macc irgazn ar ttḥucn s ifassn nɣ s tallunt.
</p>

<p>Tga <b>Wikipidya</b> yat tsanayt nɣ d asamu amuṭṭun igan ilelli nɣ aḥuṛṛi illan s kigan n <a href="/wiki/Tutlayt" title="Tutlayt">tutlayin</a>, tettuskar af ad tg yat twuri n umyawas innurẓmn i kraygatt yan, xdmn gis agudi n imaran nna gis ittaran bla zgis ɣʷin <a href="/wiki/Aqqari%E1%B8%8D" title="Aqqariḍ">tiɣrad</a>. <br><br> Wikipidya iga yan zɣ iɣbula n umlan lli kullu imqqurn d lli kullu ittussann ɣ umaḍal ɣ yigr n wantirnit, ig zɣ smmus d mraw isitn lli d bahra ttkkan middn s ussinaw lli tskr <a href="/w/index.php?title=Aliska&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Aliska (ur tlli tasna ad)">Aliska</a> ɣ wayyur n yunyu 2020. Ar takka tsanayt ad yan ukttur igan fabuṛ war asussn. Tumẓ tt <a href="/wiki/Timrslt_n_Wikimidya" title="Timrslt n Wikimidya">tmrslt n Wikimidya</a>, tettkellef sis. Tg tmrslt ad yat tmaddast mi ur igi uwttas <a href="/wiki/Aqqari%E1%B8%8D" title="Aqqariḍ">iqariḍn</a>, ar tt ttmuwwaln middn ɣar s twizi d ttabarruɛat. 
</p>

<p>Iga <b>Alugaritm agaman</b> nɣ <b>Alugaritm anipiri</b> (s <a href="/wiki/Tanglizt" class="mw-redirect" title="Tanglizt">tanglizt</a> : Natural logarithm) yat tsɣnt bahra ittyusann ɣ <a href="/wiki/Tusnakt" title="Tusnakt">tusnakt</a>. Ar tsnfal tasɣnt ad afaris s tmrnit zun d <a href="/w/index.php?title=Tas%C9%A3nt_talugaritm&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Tasɣnt talugaritm (ur tlli tasna ad)">tisɣnin ilugaritmiyn</a> yaḍnin. Ar tt nttara s mk ad : <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \ln()}">

</p><p>Ar nttini is iga alugaritm agaman s uzadur n <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle e}">

Iga alugaritm agaman tamnzut n tsɣnt : <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle x\longmapsto 1/x}">

</p><p>Alugaritm ad dars yan yism yaḍn ad t igan d "anipiri". Ism ad ikka d <a href="/wiki/John_Napir" class="mw-redirect" title="John Napir">John Napir</a>, yan umusnak askatlandi, amskar amzwaru n tflwit talugaritmiyt (tmzaray f talli nssn).
</p><p>Tettyawskar tazmilt n ulugaritm zɣ dar <a href="/w/index.php?title=Gr%C3%A9goire_de_Saint-Vincent_d_Alphonse_Antonio_de_Sarasa&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Grégoire de Saint-Vincent d Alphonse Antonio de Sarasa (ur tlli tasna ad)">Grégoire de Saint-Vincent d Alphonse Antonio de Sarasa</a> ɣ usggʷas n 1649...
(<a href="/wiki/Alugaritm_agaman" title="Alugaritm agaman"><b>Ɣr uggar</b>...</a>) 
</p>

    Kra g imnnitn nna akkʷ ifulkin g Wikipidya

    Lɛammt tga yan wanaw n tẓuṛi tamaziɣt iwtn s iẓuṛan g umzruy n ufgan amaziɣ tasut f tasut, tga taẓuṛi n uṛkaḍ imunn d nnḍm, tg s yat tgmiḍi iggutn taẓuṛi n irgazn. taẓuṛi ad tlla dar tugt n tqqbilin g Lmɣrib. Tettyussan bahra lɛammt g tqqbilt n infḍwak iwalan i tamnaḍt n Uzilal, tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifṛa. Lɛammt tga taẓuṛi iẓlin s tqqbilt n infḍwak, tlla lɛammt ula g mnnawt n tmnaḍin n tqqbilt n iɣjdamn inmalan d tqqbilt n infḍwak sg tsga n iffus utrim. . Ism ad n lɛammt illa g tmizar yaḍni zun Ẓayyan d Sus macc idrus, acku darsn anawn yaḍnin n tẓuṛi, Sus gis Aḥwac, Ẓayyan nutni ar tturarn s Uḥidus. Tettuyssan Lɛammt s ismawn yaḍni zun "Lɛmmt" d "Lɛammat".

    Ar tettyawskar Lɛammt akud nna illa kra n uzmzzu iẓlin s tqqbilt nɣ s kra n usun nɣ aḍwwaṛ, zun ig tlla tmɣra dar usli nɣ taslit, ttlgit (anmuggur da skarn middn i lɛaml, lqqayd nɣ kra n ubṛlamani) n kra wudm imqqurn, asfuglu s kra n uzmzzu n tsrtit zun istayn nɣ kra n imnɣi. G irir n Lɛammt ar ttbddadn tugt n irgazn ar skarn adur, lsn tijlluba nɣ lfuqqiyyat tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin (idrus ma g ttilint g kra n ukʷlu yaḍn), d idukan d titqacrin(ar asnt ttinin ttqqacṛ) ula nttnti g ma iggutn ar ttggant tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin, gn f yixf nnsn acddadnɣ taṛẓẓit (ar as ttinin infḍwak ṛṛẓṭ) tawṛaɣt nɣ tumlilt nɣ ar lssan f ixfawn nnsn tacacit (nɣ ṭṭagiyya) ula nttat g ukʷlu umlil nɣ awraɣ; agʷln g iɣariwn (nɣ iɣṛaḍ) nnsn lkʷmmit, ku argaz ar dis isatti allun nɣ tallunt nns nɣ ar ittḥuc ɣar s ifassn nns, yili ditsn ula bab n ganga, ar ssntayn (nɣ ar bddun) irgazn llɣa nɣ tanḍḍamt ar kkatn allun ar ig iḥma ilmma kcmn d tfrxin (ar asnt ttinin timḥwacin) ilsan lqqṭib d tmlsa tiblday n tmazirt skrnt ula nttnti adur nnsnt dat adur n irgazn macc ur a...

    Mad igan Wikipidya
    S s n f l

    Tga Wikipidya yat tsanayt nɣ d asamu amuṭṭun igan ilelli nɣ aḥuṛṛi illan s kigan n tutlayin, tettuskar af ad tg yat twuri n umyawas innurẓmn i kraygatt yan, xdmn gis agudi n imaran nna gis ittaran bla zgis ɣʷin tiɣrad.

    Wikipidya iga yan zɣ iɣbula n umlan lli kullu imqqurn d lli kullu ittussann ɣ umaḍal ɣ yigr n wantirnit, ig zɣ smmus d mraw isitn lli d bahra ttkkan middn s ussinaw lli tskr Aliska ɣ wayyur n yunyu 2020. Ar takka tsanayt ad yan ukttur igan fabuṛ war asussn. Tumẓ tt tmrslt n Wikimidya, tettkellef sis. Tg tmrslt ad yat tmaddast mi ur igi uwttas iqariḍn, ar tt ttmuwwaln middn ɣar s twizi d ttabarruɛat.

    Tamassant s tmaziɣt

    Iga Alugaritm agaman nɣ Alugaritm anipiri (s tanglizt : Natural logarithm) yat tsɣnt bahra ittyusann ɣ tusnakt. Ar tsnfal tasɣnt ad afaris s tmrnit zun d tisɣnin ilugaritmiyn yaḍnin. Ar tt nttara s mk ad : ln⁡(){\displaystyle \ln()}.

    Ar nttini is iga alugaritm agaman s uzadur n e{\displaystyle e} acku ln(e)=1{\displaystyle ln(e)=1}. Iga alugaritm agaman tamnzut n tsɣnt : x⟼1/x{\displaystyle x\longmapsto 1/x} ɣ uzilal ]0;+∞[{\displaystyle ]0;+\infty [} .

    Alugaritm ad dars yan yism yaḍn ad t igan d "anipiri". Ism ad ikka d John Napir, yan umusnak askatlandi, amskar amzwaru n tflwit talugaritmiyt (tmzaray f talli nssn).

    Tettyawskar tazmilt n ulugaritm zɣ dar Grégoire de Saint-Vincent d Alphonse Antonio de Sarasa ɣ usggʷas n 1649... (Ɣr uggar...)

Kra g imnnitn nna akkʷ ifulkin g Wikipidya

Lɛammt tga yan wanaw n tẓuṛi tamaziɣt iwtn s iẓuṛan g umzruy n ufgan amaziɣ tasut f tasut, tga taẓuṛi n uṛkaḍ imunn d nnḍm, tg s yat tgmiḍi iggutn taẓuṛi n irgazn. taẓuṛi ad tlla dar tugt n tqqbilin g Lmɣrib. Tettyussan bahra lɛammt g tqqbilt n infḍwak iwalan i tamnaḍt n Uzilal, tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifṛa. Lɛammt tga taẓuṛi iẓlin s tqqbilt n infḍwak, tlla lɛammt ula g mnnawt n tmnaḍin n tqqbilt n iɣjdamn inmalan d tqqbilt n infḍwak sg tsga n iffus utrim. . Ism ad n lɛammt illa g tmizar yaḍni zun Ẓayyan d Sus macc idrus, acku darsn anawn yaḍnin n tẓuṛi, Sus gis Aḥwac, Ẓayyan nutni ar tturarn s Uḥidus. Tettuyssan Lɛammt s ismawn yaḍni zun "Lɛmmt" d "Lɛammat".

Ar tettyawskar Lɛammt akud nna illa kra n uzmzzu iẓlin s tqqbilt nɣ s kra n usun nɣ aḍwwaṛ, zun ig tlla tmɣra dar usli nɣ taslit, ttlgit (anmuggur da skarn middn i lɛaml, lqqayd nɣ kra n ubṛlamani) n kra wudm imqqurn, asfuglu s kra n uzmzzu n tsrtit zun istayn nɣ kra n imnɣi. G irir n Lɛammt ar ttbddadn tugt n irgazn ar skarn adur, lsn tijlluba nɣ lfuqqiyyat tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin (idrus ma g ttilint g kra n ukʷlu yaḍn), d idukan d titqacrin(ar asnt ttinin ttqqacṛ) ula nttnti g ma iggutn ar ttggant tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin, gn f yixf nnsn acddad nɣ taṛẓẓit (ar as ttinin infḍwak ṛṛẓṭ) tawṛaɣt nɣ tumlilt nɣ ar lssan f ixfawn nnsn tacacit (nɣ ṭṭagiyya) ula nttat g ukʷlu umlil nɣ awraɣ; agʷln g iɣariwn (nɣ iɣṛaḍ) nnsn lkʷmmit, ku argaz ar dis isatti allun nɣ tallunt nns nɣ ar ittḥuc ɣar s ifassn nns, yili ditsn ula bab n ganga, ar ssntayn (nɣ ar bddun) irgazn llɣa nɣ tanḍḍamt ar kkatn allun ar ig iḥma ilmma kcmn d tfrxin (ar asnt ttinin timḥwacin) ilsan lqqṭib d tmlsa tiblday n tmazirt skrnt ula nttnti adur nnsnt dat adur n irgazn macc ur a ditsn ttxllaḍn ar ig ssrɣan lɛammt ilmma ku argaz ar d ilddi yat tfruxt ad dis ittḥuc. Tifrxin ar ttḥucnt s ifassn macc irgazn ar ttḥucn s ifassn nɣ s tallunt.

Tga Wikipidya yat tsanayt nɣ d asamu amuṭṭun igan ilelli nɣ aḥuṛṛi illan s kigan n tutlayin, tettuskar af ad tg yat twuri n umyawas innurẓmn i kraygatt yan, xdmn gis agudi n imaran nna gis ittaran bla zgis ɣʷin tiɣrad.

Wikipidya iga yan zɣ iɣbula n umlan lli kullu imqqurn d lli kullu ittussann ɣ umaḍal ɣ yigr n wantirnit, ig zɣ smmus d mraw isitn lli d bahra ttkkan middn s ussinaw lli tskr Aliska ɣ wayyur n yunyu 2020. Ar takka tsanayt ad yan ukttur igan fabuṛ war asussn. Tumẓ tt tmrslt n Wikimidya, tettkellef sis. Tg tmrslt ad yat tmaddast mi ur igi uwttas iqariḍn, ar tt ttmuwwaln middn ɣar s twizi d ttabarruɛat.

Amnni n imalassS s n f lKra g imnnitn nna akkʷ ifulkin g Wikipidya



Lɛammt tga yan wanaw n tẓuṛi tamaziɣt iwtn s iẓuṛan g umzruy n ufgan amaziɣ tasut f tasut, tga taẓuṛi n uṛkaḍ  imunn d nnḍm, tg s yat tgmiḍi iggutn taẓuṛi n irgazn.  taẓuṛi ad tlla dar tugt n tqqbilin g Lmɣrib. Tettyussan bahra lɛammt g tqqbilt n infḍwak iwalan i tamnaḍt n Uzilal, tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifṛa. Lɛammt tga taẓuṛi iẓlin s tqqbilt n infḍwak, tlla lɛammt ula g mnnawt n tmnaḍin n tqqbilt n iɣjdamn inmalan d tqqbilt n infḍwak sg tsga n iffus utrim. . Ism ad n lɛammt illa g tmizar yaḍni zun Ẓayyan d Sus macc idrus, acku darsn anawn yaḍnin n tẓuṛi, Sus gis Aḥwac, Ẓayyan nutni ar tturarn s Uḥidus. Tettuyssan Lɛammt s ismawn yaḍni zun "Lɛmmt" d "Lɛammat".
Ar tettyawskar Lɛammt akud nna illa kra n uzmzzu iẓlin s tqqbilt nɣ s kra n usun nɣ aḍwwaṛ, zun ig tlla tmɣra dar usli nɣ taslit, ttlgit (anmuggur da skarn middn i lɛaml, lqqayd nɣ kra n ubṛlamani) n kra wudm imqqurn, asfuglu s kra n uzmzzu n tsrtit zun istayn nɣ kra n imnɣi. G irir n Lɛammt ar ttbddadn tugt n irgazn ar skarn adur, lsn tijlluba nɣ lfuqqiyyat tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin (idrus ma g ttilint g kra n ukʷlu yaḍn), d idukan d titqacrin(ar asnt ttinin ttqqacṛ) ula nttnti g ma iggutn ar ttggant tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin, gn f yixf nnsn acddad nɣ taṛẓẓit (ar as ttinin infḍwak ṛṛẓṭ) tawṛaɣt nɣ tumlilt nɣ ar lssan f ixfawn nnsn tacacit (nɣ ṭṭagiyya) ula nttat g ukʷlu umlil nɣ awraɣ; agʷln g iɣariwn (nɣ iɣṛaḍ) nnsn lkʷmmit, ku argaz ar dis isatti allun nɣ tallunt nns nɣ ar ittḥuc ɣar s ifassn nns, yili ditsn ula bab n ganga, ar ssntayn (nɣ ar bddun) irgazn llɣa nɣ tanḍḍamt ar kkatn allun ar ig iḥma ilmma kcmn d tfrxin (ar asnt ttinin timḥwacin) ilsan lqqṭib d tmlsa tiblday n tmazirt skrnt ula nttnti adur nnsnt dat adur n irgazn macc ur a ditsn ttxllaḍn ar ig ssrɣan lɛammt ilmma ku argaz ar d ilddi yat tfruxt ad dis ittḥuc. Tifrxin ar ttḥucnt s ifassn macc irgazn ar ttḥucn s ifassn nɣ s tallunt.

Tga Wikipidya yat tsanayt nɣ d asamu amuṭṭun igan ilelli nɣ aḥuṛṛi illan s kigan n tutlayin, tettuskar af ad tg yat twuri n umyawas innurẓmn i kraygatt yan, xdmn gis agudi n imaran nna gis ittaran bla zgis ɣʷin tiɣrad.  Wikipidya iga yan zɣ iɣbula n umlan lli kullu imqqurn d lli kullu ittussann ɣ umaḍal ɣ yigr n wantirnit, ig zɣ smmus d mraw isitn lli d bahra ttkkan middn s ussinaw lli tskr Aliska ɣ wayyur n yunyu 2020. Ar takka tsanayt ad yan ukttur igan fabuṛ war asussn. Tumẓ tt tmrslt n Wikimidya, tettkellef sis. Tg tmrslt ad yat tmaddast mi ur igi uwttas iqariḍn, ar tt ttmuwwaln middn ɣar s twizi d ttabarruɛat.

**Amnni n imalass**
[ S s n f l](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tal%C9%A3a:Amgrad_ifulkin "Talɣa:Amgrad ifulkin")
  
_Kra g imnnitn nna akkʷ ifulkin g Wikipidya_
[![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/64/L%C9%9Bammt_n_i%E1%B8%A5uddjin.jpg/250px-L%C9%9Bammt_n_i%E1%B8%A5uddjin.jpg)](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afaylu:L%C9%9Bammt_n_i%E1%B8%A5uddjin.jpg)
**Lɛammt** tga yan wanaw n [tẓuṛi](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ta%E1%BA%93u%E1%B9%9Bi "Taẓuṛi") tamaziɣt iwtn s iẓuṛan g umzruy n ufgan amaziɣ tasut f tasut, tga taẓuṛi n [uṛkaḍ](https://shi.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=A%E1%B9%9Bka%E1%B8%8D&action=edit&redlink=1 "Aṛkaḍ \(ur tlli tasna ad\)") imunn d [nnḍm](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tan%E1%B8%8D%E1%B8%8Damt "Tanḍḍamt"), tg s yat tgmiḍi iggutn taẓuṛi n irgazn. taẓuṛi ad tlla dar tugt n tqqbilin g [Lmɣrib](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lm%C9%A3rib "Lmɣrib"). Tettyussan bahra lɛammt g tqqbilt n [infḍwak](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imf%E1%B8%8Dwak "Imfḍwak") iwalan i [tamnaḍt n Uzilal](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamna%E1%B8%8Dt_n_Azilal "Tamnaḍt n Azilal"), [tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifṛa](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tasga_n_Bni_Mllal-Xnifra "Tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifra"). Lɛammt tga taẓuṛi iẓlin s tqqbilt n infḍwak, tlla lɛammt ula g mnnawt n tmnaḍin n tqqbilt n [iɣjdamn](https://shi.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=I%C9%A3jdamn&action=edit&redlink=1 "Iɣjdamn \(ur tlli tasna ad\)") inmalan d tqqbilt n infḍwak sg tsga n iffus utrim. . Ism ad n lɛammt illa g tmizar yaḍni zun [Ẓayyan](https://shi.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E1%BA%92ayyan&action=edit&redlink=1 "Ẓayyan \(ur tlli tasna ad\)") d [Sus](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sus "Sus") macc idrus, acku darsn anawn yaḍnin n tẓuṛi, Sus gis [Aḥwac](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/A%E1%B8%A5wac "Aḥwac"), Ẓayyan nutni ar tturarn s [Uḥidus](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/A%E1%B8%A5idus "Aḥidus"). Tettuyssan Lɛammt s ismawn yaḍni zun "Lɛmmt" d "Lɛammat". 
Ar tettyawskar Lɛammt akud nna illa kra n uzmzzu iẓlin s tqqbilt nɣ s kra n usun nɣ aḍwwaṛ, zun ig tlla tmɣra dar usli nɣ taslit, ttlgit (anmuggur da skarn middn i lɛaml, lqqayd nɣ kra n ubṛlamani) n kra wudm imqqurn, asfuglu s kra n uzmzzu n tsrtit zun istayn nɣ kra n [imnɣi](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imn%C9%A3i "Imnɣi"). G irir n Lɛammt ar ttbddadn tugt n irgazn ar skarn adur, lsn [tijlluba](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tajllabit "Tajllabit") nɣ lfuqqiyyat tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin (idrus ma g ttilint g kra n ukʷlu yaḍn), d [idukan](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aduku "Aduku") d titqacrin(ar asnt ttinin ttqqacṛ) ula nttnti g ma iggutn ar ttggant tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin, gn f yixf nnsn [acddad](https://shi.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Acddad&action=edit&redlink=1 "Acddad \(ur tlli tasna ad\)") nɣ taṛẓẓit (ar as ttinin infḍwak ṛṛẓṭ) tawṛaɣt nɣ tumlilt nɣ ar lssan f ixfawn nnsn tacacit (nɣ ṭṭagiyya) ula nttat g ukʷlu umlil nɣ awraɣ; agʷln g iɣariwn (nɣ iɣṛaḍ) nnsn lkʷmmit, ku argaz ar dis isatti allun nɣ tallunt nns nɣ ar ittḥuc ɣar s ifassn nns, yili ditsn ula bab n ganga, ar ssntayn (nɣ ar bddun) irgazn llɣa nɣ tanḍḍamt ar kkatn allun ar ig iḥma ilmma kcmn d tfrxin (ar asnt ttinin timḥwacin) ilsan lqqṭib d tmlsa tiblday n tmazirt skrnt ula nttnti adur nnsnt dat adur n irgazn macc ur a ditsn ttxllaḍn ar ig ssrɣan lɛammt ilmma ku argaz ar d ilddi yat tfruxt ad dis ittḥuc. Tifrxin ar ttḥucnt s ifassn macc irgazn ar ttḥucn s ifassn nɣ s tallunt.

Wikipidya iga yan zɣ iɣbula n umlan lli kullu imqqurn d lli kullu ittussann ɣ umaḍal ɣ yigr n wantirnit, ig zɣ smmus d mraw isitn lli d bahra ttkkan middn s ussinaw lli tskr [Aliska](https://shi.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Aliska&action=edit&redlink=1 "Aliska \(ur tlli tasna ad\)") ɣ wayyur n yunyu 2020. Ar takka tsanayt ad yan ukttur igan fabuṛ war asussn. Tumẓ tt [tmrslt n Wikimidya](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timrslt_n_Wikimidya "Timrslt n Wikimidya"), tettkellef sis. Tg tmrslt ad yat tmaddast mi ur igi uwttas [iqariḍn](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aqqari%E1%B8%8D "Aqqariḍ"), ar tt ttmuwwaln middn ɣar s twizi d ttabarruɛat.

Iga **Alugaritm agaman** nɣ **Alugaritm anipiri** (s [tanglizt](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tanglizt "Tanglizt") : Natural logarithm) yat tsɣnt bahra ittyusann ɣ [tusnakt](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tusnakt "Tusnakt"). Ar tsnfal tasɣnt ad afaris s tmrnit zun d [tisɣnin ilugaritmiyn](https://shi.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Tas%C9%A3nt_talugaritm&action=edit&redlink=1 "Tasɣnt talugaritm \(ur tlli tasna ad\)") yaḍnin. Ar tt nttara s mk ad :  ln ⁡ ( ) {\displaystyle \ln()} ![{\\displaystyle \\ln\(\)}](https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/ba402812c9973ae68ba7d44de83b26f4b9692480). 
Ar nttini is iga alugaritm agaman s uzadur n  e {\displaystyle e} ![{\\displaystyle e}](https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/cd253103f0876afc68ebead27a5aa9867d927467) acku  l n ( e ) = 1 {\displaystyle ln(e)=1} ![{\\displaystyle ln\(e\)=1}](https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/307803c026addf230fe82554150bdc7ecf54933a). Iga alugaritm agaman tamnzut n tsɣnt :  x ⟼ 1 / x {\displaystyle x\longmapsto 1/x} ![{\\displaystyle x\\longmapsto 1/x}](https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/21f400318a02abd1e444e7a764da7323e4edd62b) ɣ uzilal  ] 0 ; + ∞ [ {\displaystyle ]0;+\infty [} ![{\\displaystyle \]0;+\\infty \[}](https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/9a2b9afa8192cc3f8173fadddad0d1f5c499d881) . 
Alugaritm ad dars yan yism yaḍn ad t igan d "anipiri". Ism ad ikka d [John Napir](https://shi.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Napir "John Napir"), yan umusnak askatlandi, amskar amzwaru n tflwit talugaritmiyt (tmzaray f talli nssn). 
Tettyawskar tazmilt n ulugaritm zɣ dar [Grégoire de Saint-Vincent d Alphonse Antonio de Sarasa](https://shi.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Gr%C3%A9goire_de_Saint-Vincent_d_Alphonse_Antonio_de_Sarasa&action=edit&redlink=1 "Grégoire de Saint-Vincent d Alphonse Antonio de Sarasa \(ur tlli tasna ad\)") ɣ usggʷas n 1649... **Lɛammt** tga yan wanaw n tẓuṛi⟨81⟩ tamaziɣt iwtn s iẓuṛan g umzruy n ufgan amaziɣ tasut f tasut, tga taẓuṛi n uṛkaḍ⟨82⟩ imunn d nnḍm⟨83⟩, tg s yat tgmiḍi iggutn taẓuṛi n irgazn. taẓuṛi ad tlla dar tugt n tqqbilin g Lmɣrib⟨84⟩. Tettyussan bahra lɛammt g tqqbilt n infḍwak⟨85⟩ iwalan i tamnaḍt n Uzilal⟨86⟩, tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifṛa⟨87⟩. Lɛammt tga taẓuṛi iẓlin s tqqbilt n infḍwak, tlla lɛammt ula g mnnawt n tmnaḍin n tqqbilt n iɣjdamn⟨88⟩ inmalan d tqqbilt n infḍwak sg tsga n iffus utrim. . Ism ad n lɛammt illa g tmizar yaḍni zun Ẓayyan⟨89⟩ d Sus⟨90⟩ macc idrus, acku darsn anawn yaḍnin n tẓuṛi, Sus gis Aḥwac⟨91⟩, Ẓayyan nutni ar tturarn s Uḥidus⟨92⟩. Tettuyssan Lɛammt s ismawn yaḍni zun "Lɛmmt" d "Lɛammat". 
Ar tettyawskar Lɛammt akud nna illa kra n uzmzzu iẓlin s tqqbilt nɣ s kra n usun nɣ aḍwwaṛ, zun ig tlla tmɣra dar usli nɣ taslit, ttlgit (anmuggur da skarn middn i lɛaml, lqqayd nɣ kra n ubṛlamani) n kra wudm imqqurn, asfuglu s kra n uzmzzu n tsrtit zun istayn nɣ kra n imnɣi⟨93⟩. G irir n Lɛammt ar ttbddadn tugt n irgazn ar skarn adur, lsn tijlluba⟨94⟩ nɣ lfuqqiyyat tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin (idrus ma g ttilint g kra n ukʷlu yaḍn), d idukan⟨95⟩ d titqacrin(ar asnt ttinin ttqqacṛ) ula nttnti g ma iggutn ar ttggant tumlilin nɣ tiwraɣin, gn f yixf nnsn acddad⟨96⟩ nɣ taṛẓẓit (ar as ttinin infḍwak ṛṛẓṭ) tawṛaɣt nɣ tumlilt nɣ ar lssan f ixfawn nnsn tacacit (nɣ ṭṭagiyya) ula nttat g ukʷlu umlil nɣ awraɣ; agʷln g iɣariwn (nɣ iɣṛaḍ) nnsn lkʷmmit, ku argaz ar dis isatti allun nɣ tallunt nns nɣ ar ittḥuc ɣar s ifassn nns, yili ditsn ula bab n ganga, ar ssntayn (nɣ ar bddun) irgazn llɣa nɣ tanḍḍamt ar kkatn allun ar ig iḥma ilmma kcmn d tfrxin (ar asnt ttinin timḥwacin) ilsan lqqṭib d tmlsa tiblday n tmazirt skrnt ula nttnti adur nnsnt dat adur n irgazn macc ur a ditsn ttxllaḍn ar ig ssrɣan lɛammt ilmma ku argaz ar d ilddi yat tfruxt ad dis ittḥuc.
